the control attribute specifies that the audio controls should be dispayed such as play/pause etc
the loop attribute it specifies that the audio will start over again every time it ends
the src the url of the audio file
-->

<!--there are 3 supported file formats....mp3-mimetype is audio/mpeg....ogg-mimetype is audio/ogg....wav-mimetype is audio/wav-->

